New Records: Jordan Cox, Jacob Bethell, and Jamie Overton made their T20I debuts for England.
Jos Buttler was ruled out due to a calf injury, making Jamie Overton his replacement in the XI.
Pre-Game Insights: Phil Salt was named the captain of the England XI for the match.
Jos Buttler's calf injury led to Harry Brook being the stand-in captain with Jordan Cox added as cover.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was set to be played in Southampton on September 11, 2024.
The England XI included several notable players like Will Jacks, Sam Curran, and Jofra Archer.
